{"tid":1715763,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"[緊急] 唔想中大手足少個機會比人告暴動入黎","createTime":"2019-11-13T07:20:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-13T09:29:55.000Z","uid":64946,"like":23,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"44210f77aaceea4943bea28f1dee368aa5b88d9f","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:20:58.000Z","msg":"利申返自己係IT白痴<br />\n都係盡我所能出idea 比手足<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n已經打左差唔多三日 都知你地好攰 <br />\nin case 比人攻入 or 秋後 <br />\n告入暴動就坐10 年<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n強烈建議各位返各大buildings到<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">破壞cctv </span></strong></span><br />\n有部分cctv 係local 黎 <br />\n打爛就冇底<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n尤其係自己地頭 <br />\nbb 可能做得比較鬆懈<br />\n你地成日走黎走去 又做魔法材料<br />\n真係要小心啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中大太多cctv 我講唔到邊啲係local 邊啲係cloud <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>總之打爛hard disk / del record前 <br />\n記得保護好身份</strong></span><br />\n</span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: teal;\">建議</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">1. </span>情況許可/有需要的話 自己先留一份copy <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">2. </span>係隱蔽位置裝返自己嘅cctv <br />\n(up 上cloud 個種，保障自己） <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\">3. </span>打開有前置鏡頭嘅電腦錄影 <br />\n(save 係cloud)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">但係<br />\n冇左cctv 之後啲狗可能會更放肆咁去打死人<br />\n手足要衡量完風險再決定打唔打爛<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n</span></strong><br />\n</span></span></span><br />\n <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n諗諗下都係覺得唔應該打爛 <br />\n大家千其唔好咁做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bab4518c687364179e94cd734e0d0a09afe3a4f","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:22:02.000Z","msg":"diu 打錯標題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n係唔想中大手足多個機會比人告先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1c27a177aee15c4081cb5b9b2cf9c841c450be6","tid":1715763,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"683cc327a619d20a59e3bdafd241974ef75f5ba5","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1c27a177aee15c4081cb5b9b2cf9c841c450be6","tid":1715763,"uid":258598,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:23:54.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:25:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a3f7e2977487ffe3e3f768cce021a3e3e7ee9d1","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:26:42.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d933039c0713a20d31d8eb2ad33ecb4933e41d5d","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:27:49.000Z","msg":"pishhh"},{"pid":"7f4cb5c290e57b6bd75d73b57467f81b7035a82c","tid":1715763,"uid":64946,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:30:16.000Z","msg":"pish"},{"pid":"538a3857131070f42f3f36e230cdedafc2de0dde","tid":1715763,"uid":88141,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T07:32:10.000Z","msg":"咁黑心 唔準推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pi